         MACRO
         PLITCA
TCA      DSECT ,        PL/I TCA (ADDRESSED BY R12)
         SPACE
TFB0     EQU   TCA      FIRST FLAG BYTE
TTCK     EQU   X'20'    CHECKOUT COMPILER ENVIRONMENT
TTFC     EQU   X'04'    CICS ENVIRONMENT (USED BY LIE TO INDICATE      *
                        ASSEMBLER PSEUDO-PL/I ENVIRONMENT)
TFB1     EQU   TCA+1    SECOND FLAG BYTE
TGFS     EQU   X'10'    PLISORT ACTIVE (INHIBIT GOTO OUT OF BLOCK)
TPRV     EQU   TCA+4    PSEUDO-REGISTER VECTOR POINTER
TEOS     EQU   TCA+12   END OF CURRENT STORAGE SEGMENT
TOVV     EQU   TCA+72   VDA STORAGE OVERFLOW ROUTINE
TGET     EQU   TCA+108  NON-LIFO STORAGE GET ROUTINE
TFRE     EQU   TCA+112  NON-LIFO STORAGE FREE ROUTINE
TOVF     EQU   TCA+116  DSA STORAGE OVERFLOW ROUTINE
TERR     EQU   TCA+120  PL/I ERROR HANDLER ADDRESS
TGTC     EQU   TCA+128  GOTO OUT OF BLOCK CODE
TUSR     EQU   TCA+X'11C'    TCA USER FIELD
TATP     EQU   TCA+X'120'    OPTIMIZER ATTN POLL ROUTINE ADDR
TGAR     EQU   TCA+X'190'    CHECKER GETMAIN ASSURANCE ROUTINE
TFRR     EQU   TCA+X'194'    CHECKER FREEMAIN RECOVERY ROUTINE
ZCTLB1   EQU   TCA+X'AD6'    CHECKER FLAGS
ZATTN    EQU   X'10'    CHECKER ATTN PENDING
         MEND
